    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It is functional but has significant mechanical issues that will require attention, along with heavy exterior wear including deep scratches, dents, and faded or damaged paint. The interior is heavily worn with noticeable damage to surfaces and components. This vehicle is best suited for someone willing to invest in repairs or looking for a parts car.",
